{"blogid": "123328891", "writerAge": "码龄1年", "writerBlogNum": "17", "writerCollect": "286", "writerComment": "650", "writerFan": "1804", "writerGrade": "4级", "writerIntegral": "1231", "writerName": "想要慢慢变得优秀的向阳同学", "writerProfileAdress": "..\\..\\static\\writer_image\\profile_123328891.jpg", "writerRankTotal": "74551", "writerRankWeekly": "213544", "writerThumb": "533", "writerVisitNum": "21078", "blog_read_count": "2391", "blog_time": "已于 2022-03-07 20:05:16 修改", "blog_title": "【C和指针】带你领略C语言最有灵魂的内容（上）", "content": "<div class=\"article_content clearfix\" id=\"article_content\">\n<link href=\"../../static/bootstrap/css/csdnstyle.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\"/>\n<div class=\"htmledit_views\" id=\"content_views\">\n<p><strong>        大家好😃，我是<span style=\"color:#4da8ee;\">想要慢慢变得优秀的向阳🌞同学👨‍💻</span>，从今天开始逐渐恢复更新状态，想学习计算机知识的小伙伴可以支持一下哦！~不能说肯定是干货，但会让你有所收获！</strong>💓💓💓</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">🍭🍭<strong>快乐地生活在这个世界上，你不需要取悦于任何人，做最好的自己。</strong>🍭🍭</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p id=\"main-toc\"><strong>目录</strong></p>\n<p id=\"%F0%9F%A7%85%F0%9F%A7%85%E6%8C%87%E9%92%88%E7%B1%BB%E5%9E%8B%F0%9F%A7%85%F0%9F%A7%85-toc\" style=\"margin-left:0px;\"><a href=\"#%F0%9F%A7%85%F0%9F%A7%85%E6%8C%87%E9%92%88%E7%B1%BB%E5%9E%8B%F0%9F%A7%85%F0%9F%A7%85\">🧅🧅指针类型🧅🧅</a></p>\n<p id=\"%F0%9F%8D%86%F0%9F%8D%86%E6%A1%88%E4%BE%8B1%EF%BC%9A%F0%9F%8D%86%F0%9F%8D%86-toc\" style=\"margin-left:40px;\"><a href=\"#%F0%9F%8D%86%F0%9F%8D%86%E6%A1%88%E4%BE%8B1%EF%BC%9A%F0%9F%8D%86%F0%9F%8D%86\">🍆🍆案例1：🍆🍆</a></p>\n<p id=\"%F0%9F%A5%94%F0%9F%A5%94%E6%A1%88%E4%BE%8B%E4%BA%8C%EF%BC%9A%F0%9F%A5%94%F0%9F%A5%94-toc\" style=\"margin-left:40px;\"><a href=\"#%F0%9F%A5%94%F0%9F%A5%94%E6%A1%88%E4%BE%8B%E4%BA%8C%EF%BC%9A%F0%9F%A5%94%F0%9F%A5%94\">🥔🥔案例二：🥔🥔</a></p>\n<p id=\"%F0%9F%8D%84%F0%9F%8D%84%E6%8C%87%E9%92%88%E5%92%8C%E6%95%B0%E7%BB%84%F0%9F%8D%84%F0%9F%8D%84-toc\" style=\"margin-left:0px;\"><a href=\"#%F0%9F%8D%84%F0%9F%8D%84%E6%8C%87%E9%92%88%E5%92%8C%E6%95%B0%E7%BB%84%F0%9F%8D%84%F0%9F%8D%84\">🍄🍄指针和数组🍄🍄</a>